  <TITLE>Product reviews per store</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>Public store. But we should make it configurable &gt; catalog settings &gt; &quot;reviews per store&quot; (disabled by default). This setting will indicate whether displayed reviews in public store should be filtered by the current store or all reviews should be displayed Admin area. We also have to display the store in which a review has been written on the review list page in admin area (http://admin-demo.nopcommerce.com/Admin/ProductReview/List). Let's also add a &quot;Store&quot; dropdownlist to filter reviews by store Source: http://www.nopcommerce.com/boards/t/36808/productreview.aspx</DESCRIPTION>
